examples.en: Their sources of finance are drying up.
Taking too much water for household use is drying up the river.
He was drying his hair with a towel.
He's been drying out at a private clinic.
For drying grass seed, the in-sack drier had many advantages.
Your shirt is drying on the clothesline.
Usually the driftwood is so logged with water that it needs an extended drying period before it can be used by the artist.
